item.title: Time To Move on
item.description: References TTC The Great War (Liulevicius) BBC Bitesize If you are not moving forward you are regressing. 9 years in one school 192*4 768 768 lessons per years 6912 lessons So first i was rejected for an SLT position, i am still early in my career but an interview would have been nice. “France sought allies with which to oppose Germany.” (Liulevicius :161)
